effect:
Become _Charging_ until the end of the _Phase_. While _Charging_, your space and all adjacent spaces are _Electrified_ and you gain _Stormwalk_. After removing _Charging_ your next _Storm_ Attack either makes all spaces in the _Area_ _Electrified_ or creates _Electrified_ spaces in a Target's space and all adjacent spaces.
&nbsp;
You only gain this benefit if you lose _Charging_ at the end of _Phase_, not if you lose it due to _Break_ or other similar effects.
